  <prompt>
    Implement FileIndexingService with three entry points converging to a shared pipeline.
    The service should: download file (OBO or app-only), extract text, chunk text using
    ITextChunkingService, generate embeddings, and index via IRagService.IndexDocumentsBatchAsync.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in RAG pipelines, Azure OpenAI embeddings, and
    Azure AI Search indexing. Follow ADR-007 for file access and ADR-013 for AI architecture.
  </role>

  <goal>
    FileIndexingService fully implemented with three entry points producing identical results.
    Service integrates with TextExtractor, TextChunkingService, EmbeddingCache, and RagService.
  </goal>

  <context>
